"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"This is an oh-so-good recipe. Just the right amount of spice to make you take a cold drink but definitely keep coming back for more! This soup is irresistible!\\n\\n[ \\n ](https://www.allrecipes.com/cook/2394219/)Step 1\\n\\nCook the Italian sausage and red pepper flakes in a Dutch oven over medium-high heat until crumbly, browned, and no longer pink, 10 to 15 minutes. Drain and set aside.\\n\\n* Step 2\\n\\n  Cook the bacon in the same Dutch oven over medium heat until crisp, about 10 minutes. Drain, leaving a few tablespoons of drippings with the bacon in the bottom of the Dutch oven. Stir in the onions and garlic; cook until onions are soft and translucent, about 5 minutes.\\n* Step 3\\n\\n  Pour the chicken broth into the Dutch oven with the bacon and onion mixture; bring to a boil over high heat. Add the potatoes, and boil until fork tender, about 20 minutes. Reduce the heat to medium and stir in the heavy cream and the cooked sausage; heat through. Mix the spinach into the soup just before serving.\",\"timestamp\":1640335212,\"title\":\"Super-Delicious Zuppa Toscana\"},\"digest\":\"IDrnk6nhdGgbGahD50Dmxwdg_GOPfWpjirHTPGqO0Xk\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xC44d7D9C6cB148d8621328fc1F5d3893126e6968\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"6sOe1fSlqYeTX-QWBAajJxqyEb1md3PDbkbpUXRJNn8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"CmwpZ8Y81q6j7zi6979-0DqAlh5PS_RqQ_WQv-Lr4a8\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"EM-A4prajxsDKCWW1RAS43wRg5-Tffh-Ykic6las1Y8rvs0U0X6Z6AGAiQDXXTfUHFWDoOxJG8spZxvUjpKDLQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x976ab3bb765e15fb5353e17a658cd3aff15b2e7e593a684424e5b10a880111707b3c648ae7dd21e06d2a4c618dc9c377961fd47688d982bea14fa2dea8f1864d1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"6sOe1fSlqYeTX-QWBAajJxqyEb1md3PD